        p Have the opportunity to lead a team of talented designers and guide the direction of new products and refresh existing products and pages. I can to Ticketmaster as a contractor to help with a specific project but wound up loving the people and culture and decided to join full time.
      section.grid
        .half
          h2.themeBackground Making the Connection
          p Linking millions of accounts is a delicate process, especially without an option to undo.
          p Merging millions of accounts is more complicated than it sounds... Over 900 season ticket sites had their own authentication not tied to Ticketmaster. For future products to function they needed to be brought into the Ticketmaster ecosystem. This meant a progressive rollout to over a million active accounts during the off season for each sports team and theatre. 
          p The main challenge for this project was not the front end, but how to manage several dozen edge cases that could potentially keep a fan from attending their favorite game or performance.
