        h2.themeBackground Virtual Venue
        p Early in the design process we knew we wanted to validate some key interaction assumptions before diving too deep into design. Because traditional clickable prototypes like Invision wouldn't suffice in mocking up interactions, I chose to use Framer for the interactive prototype. This allowed us to quickly code up interactions without building a whole interactive site. Because our design system is React based, we could quickly import the actual assets into Framer for realistic design and interactivity. In testing with real season ticket holders, the reactions were fantastic and helped us validate our assumptions and gain a better understanding of what future features fans would like to see.
